<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>505 Cafe | تجربة القهوة العصرية</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Tajawal & Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        /* --- APPLE DESIGN SYSTEM VARIABLES --- */
        :root {
            --apple-bg: #ffffff;
            --apple-bg-secondary: #f5f5f7;
            --apple-text: #1d1d1f;
            --apple-text-secondary: #86868b;
            --apple-text-tertiary: #6e6e73;
            --apple-blue: #0071e3;
            --apple-blue-hover: #0077ed;
            --apple-border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --apple-card-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            --apple-transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            --royal-blue: #12308c;
        }

        /* --- BASIC RESET & TYPOGRAPHY --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Tajawal', 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--apple-bg);
            color: var(--apple-text);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- APPLE MINIMALIST SCROLLBAR --- */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #d2d2d7;
            border-radius: 99px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--apple-text-secondary);
        }

        /* --- NAVIGATION BAR --- */
        nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            height: 52px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 40px;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--apple-text);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .nav-brand span {
            background: var(--apple-text);
            color: var(--apple-bg);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: monospace;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .nav-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .cart-trigger {
            position: relative;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
            padding: 6px;
        }

        .cart-trigger:hover {
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .cart-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -4px;
            background: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transform: scale(0);
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .cart-badge.active {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .instagram-top {
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .instagram-top:hover {
            color: #e1306c;
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at bottom, #ffffff 0%, var(--apple-bg-secondary) 100%);
            padding: 100px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
        }

        .hero-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--apple-text);
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--apple-blue);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            max-width: 550px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 350;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 113, 227, 0.15);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--apple-blue-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            color: var(--apple-text);
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        /* --- CAROUSEL SECTION --- */
        .carousel-section {
            padding: 80px 40px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .section-header {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .section-title p {
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .carousel-controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .carousel-btn {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            color: var(--apple-text);
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .carousel-btn:hover {
            background: #e8e8ed;
        }

        .carousel-wrapper {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .carousel-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            padding: 10px 0 30px 0;
        }

        .carousel-container::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        .carousel-card {
            min-width: 320px;
            width: 320px;
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border-radius: 28px;
            overflow: hidden;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .carousel-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: var(--apple-card-shadow);
        }

        .card-img-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            height: 240px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            
            object-position: center;
            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        .carousel-card:hover .card-img {
            transform: scale(1.06);
        }

        .card-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            right: 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            color: var(--apple-text);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .card-content {
            padding: 24px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--apple-text);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            height: 36px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: -webkit-box;
            
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        }

        .card-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .card-price {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .card-price span {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .btn-add-cart {
            background: var(--apple-text);
            color: var(--apple-bg);
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .btn-add-cart:hover {
            background: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
        }

        /* --- MAIN MENU SECTION --- */
        .menu-section {
            padding: 100px 40px;
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
        }

        .tabs-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }

        .tabs-container::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            border: none;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .tab-btn.active {
            background: var(--apple-text);
            color: var(--apple-bg);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .menu-grid {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .menu-item-card {
            background: var(--apple-bg);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .menu-item-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--apple-card-shadow);
        }

        .item-img-container {
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .item-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .menu-item-card:hover .item-img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .item-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--apple-text);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .item-desc {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            height: 32px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: -webkit-box;
          
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        }

        .item-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        /* --- CART PANEL (Apple Tray Style) --- */
        .cart-panel {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            background: var(--apple-bg);
            box-shadow: -10px 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            z-index: 150;
            transform: translateX(-100%);
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .cart-panel.open {
            transform: translateX(0);
        }

        .cart-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            z-index: 140;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
        }

        .cart-overlay.open {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .cart-header {
            padding: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cart-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .close-cart {
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border: none;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .close-cart:hover {
            background: #e8e8ed;
        }

        .cart-items-wrapper {
            flex-grow: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .cart-empty {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
        }

        .cart-empty i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #d2d2d7;
        }

        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
        }

        .cart-item-img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .cart-item-details {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .cart-item-name {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .cart-item-price {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .cart-qty-control {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .qty-btn {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cart-footer {
            padding: 24px;
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .total-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .total-val {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--apple-text);
        }

        .btn-checkout {
            width: 100%;
            background: #25d366; /* WhatsApp color */
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.2);
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .btn-checkout:hover {
            background: #20ba59;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* --- FLOATING CART BUTTON --- */
        .floating-cart {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            left: 24px;
            background: var(--apple-text);
            color: var(--apple-bg);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            z-index: 120;
            transform: translateY(100px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .floating-cart.visible {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .floating-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            background: var(--apple-blue);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* --- TOAST NOTIFICATIONS --- */
        .toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 32px;
            right: 32px;
            background: var(--apple-text);
            color: var(--apple-bg);
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transform: translateY(100px);
            opacity: 0;
            z-index: 200;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .toast.show {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            background: var(--apple-bg-secondary);
            padding: 80px 40px 40px 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--apple-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--apple-transition);
        }

        .social-icon:hover {
            color: #e1306c;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--apple-card-shadow);
        }

        .social-icon.whatsapp:hover {
            color: #25d366;
        }

        .copyright {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--apple-text-secondary);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--apple-border);
            padding-top: 32px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        /* --- RESPONSIVENESS --- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav {
                padding: 0 20px;
            }
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.25rem;
                letter-spacing: -0.8px;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
            .section-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 16px;
            }
            .carousel-section {
                padding: 60px 20px;
            }
            .menu-section {
                padding: 60px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVIGATION BAR -->
    <nav>
        <a href="#" class="nav-brand">
            <span>505</span> CAFE
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#home">الرئيسية</a></li>
            <li><a href="#special-offers">الأكثر تميزاً</a></li>
            <li><a href="#menu-section">القائمة الكاملة</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="nav-actions">
            <button class="cart-trigger" onclick="toggleCart()">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bag-shopping"></i>
                <span class="cart-badge" id="nav-cart-badge">0</span>
            </button>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank" class="instagram-top">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <span class="hero-tag">الجيل الثالث من القهوة المختصة</span>
        <h1>مذاق غني في كل <span>تفصيلة</span></h1>
        <p>في 505 Cafe، نسكب الحُب والتركيز في كل كوب. صُمم المنيو الخاص بنا بعناية ليجمع أفضل حبوب البن الفاخرة والنكهات الاستثنائية الحالمة.</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="#menu-section" class="btn-primary">تصفح المنيو</a>
            <a href="#special-offers" class="btn-secondary">الأكثر طلباً</a>
        </div>
